We've had complaints that users are unable to find the "Create a request" link without going several clicks deep. This particular use case occurs when viewing items in the portal. It's not particularly efficient. 

Ultimately, if a button could be added in the header beside the "Requests" button, it would make much more sense and save our users the confusion of trying to find a link to open a new request.

