When running a Service Desk handling requests regarding software packages, the versions field is a field that is convenient to use as an indicator in the request itself.
Currently, versions are a project wide field, which means that if a Service Desk handles multiple software packages, all their combined versions will get displayed as possible values for the field.
Being able to segment the available versions based on request type, or the value of another field, would greatly improve the read and usability of the versions field.

